          0,
          "It’s been more than 15 years since Capcom rebooted the "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Resident Evil"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " franchise (for the first time) with the release of "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Resident Evil 4"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " in 2005. I for one was pretty gutted to see this revolution happen because "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Resident Evil 1 and 2"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " are still, to this day, some of my favourite games of all time. To that end, when I heard about "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Tormented Souls"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " and its promise to harken back to the PlayStation 1 "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Resident Evil "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "days of old, I was delighted! "
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      10,
      0
    ],
