      1
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Now that I have a young son, I tend to only get time to play video games late at night after he’s gone to bed - I’m a scaredy cat at the best of times but this was NOT a good idea when playing "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Tormented Souls"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ". The story is predominantly set in a creepy old hospital (think the mansion in "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "RE1"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " and the police station in "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "RE2"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "), and your character, Caroline Walker, gets inextricably involved when she wakes up in one of the hospital bathrooms with no idea how she got there. She then begins to unfurl the mystery of two missing girls who appear to have been patients there in the past. The story is even more unsettling than some of the old "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Resident Evil"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " fare, so if you’re a fan of gore, jump scares and general moribund shenanigans, then you’ll love "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Tormented Souls"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "The hospital acts as a kind of Metroidvania type world where you need to find keys and other items to unlock paths (yes, there’s a fair bit of backtracking). There is a lot of puzzle solving which involves inspecting items in your inventory and working out where the best place to use them is. If you’ve played the old "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "Resident Evil"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " games, you’ll know all the old tricks to look out for, but if you’re new to the genre, you may find some of the puzzles slightly too abstract and complex."
        ]
      ]
    ],
